data.description: Set on a private corner lot this well-built home needs just a little TLC to make it shine: New roof in 2020, new water heater & furnace in 2023. Now the home only needs interior paint & carpet/flooring to make it like new and build your equity. The home is priced with the carpet and interior paint in mind which will give you equity for little effort. The large primary suite is separated from the two secondary bedrooms by the large living rm, family rm & kitchen. The large level, corner lot offers great privacy & space for gardening & Yard games. Large outbuilding included. There is even some tree filtered views of Bellingham, the Bay & the islands from the home & Yard. Great opportunity for building equity in a wonderful home in Bellingham
